    "description": "In Quandary, a moral dilemma unfolds. As a doctor facing an unimaginable choice, you must make your emotional and logical self cooperate to find a solution, even when the law offers no answers.<br><br>Quandary is an intriguing 2D puzzle platformer where your character's internal struggle is brought to life. Your logic and empathy take form as two separate characters, <strong>moving in opposite directions, forcing you to strategically utilize both to navigate challenging puzzles</strong>. <br><br><strong>Can you find harmony within this chaos and solve puzzles that seem impossible, ultimately deciding the fate of your suffering patient?</strong><br><br><strong>You control two bodies that move in opposite directions!</strong><br>You control two bodies that move in opposite directions and represent your empathy and logic. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050830/extras/f193dc8bf51d8f07416ebbc03512075a.poster.avif?t=1721982584\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050830/extras/f193dc8bf51d8f07416ebbc03512075a.webm?t=1721982584\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050830/extras/f193dc8bf51d8f07416ebbc03512075a.mp4?t=1721982584\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Follow the light with your conscience!</strong><br>Solve puzzles to reach the light.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050830/extras/ef6c7ebdd71ca9d48ebb97afd511100e.poster.avif?t=1721982584\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050830/extras/ef6c7ebdd71ca9d48ebb97afd511100e.webm?t=1721982584\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050830/extras/ef6c7ebdd71ca9d48ebb97afd511100e.mp4?t=1721982584\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Make your logic and empathy cooperate! </strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050830/extras/f0445afb58cc25fb0ef1335d497cefbb.poster.avif?t=1721982584\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050830/extras/f0445afb58cc25fb0ef1335d497cefbb.webm?t=1721982584\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050830/extras/f0445afb58cc25fb0ef1335d497cefbb.mp4?t=1721982584\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>If he dies, you die.</strong><br>Duh, he is you, and you are him...<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050830/extras/8a44c03a354e420c030522090d2be5d6.poster.avif?t=1721982584\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050830/extras/8a44c03a354e420c030522090d2be5d6.webm?t=1721982584\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050830/extras/8a44c03a354e420c030522090d2be5d6.mp4?t=1721982584\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Join Our Discord</h2>",
